text: Skopkortnaya () is a rural locality (a settlement) and the administrative center of Skopkortnenskoye Rural Settlement, Alexandrovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 335 as of 2010.ВПН-2010. Численность и размещение населения Пермского края There are 13 streets. == References == Category:Rural localities in Alexandrovsky District
